hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: We've got a joint account easterncarolinamedicine.org I think we forget, that until modern times, a lot of people lived like this. 200 or maybe even 100 years ago, a lot of people lived off the land in conditions we'd describe as deplorable now. Of course, a lot of those people died during the winter, or due to conditions relating to poor hygine, but the point is that the lifestyle these people have decided to live isn't new.
